Smart Balance Academy

Smart Balance Academy is a modern AI-powered learning and business platform focused on technology, entrepreneurship, coding, AI automation, branding, and digital innovation in South Sudan and Africa.

Vision

To empower the next generation of African innovators, developers, creators, and startup founders.

Features

- AI learning systems
- Coding courses
- Startup incubation
- Digital branding
- Automation tools
- Mobile & web apps

Tech Stack

- React
- Next.js
- Tailwind CSS
- Node.js
- Firebase
- OpenAI APIs

Founder

Matthew Awane

Future Goals

- Launch full academy platform
- Build AI CEO systems
- Create startup ecosystem
- Expand globally
